---
  <!-- ========== WHY CHOOSE US ========== -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 fade-in">
        <div class="inline-block bg-[#00A9E0]/10 text-[#00A9E0] px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-4">
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold">¿POR QUÉ ELEGIRNOS?</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          Ventajas que nos hacen únicos
        </h3>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center fade-in">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 gradient-racing rounded-2xl mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M11.99 2C6.47 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.47 10 9.99 10C17.52 22 22 17.52 22 12S17.52 2 11.99 2zM12 20c-4.42 0-8-3.58-8-8s3.58-8 8-8 8 3.58 8 8-3.58 8-8 8zm.5-13H11v6l5.25 3.15.75-1.23-4.5-2.67z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Cumplimos o te avisamos</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Si hay un imprevisto, te llamamos antes de que nos preguntes</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center fade-in">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 gradient-racing rounded-2xl mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M18 8h-1V6c0-2.76-2.24-5-5-5S7 3.24 7 6v2H6c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v10c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h12c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V10c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm-6 9c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2s.9-2 2-2 2 .9 2 2-.9 2-2 2zm3.1-9H8.9V6c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1 1.71 0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1v2z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">100% Asegurado</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Cada carga viaja protegida. Si algo pasa, respondemos</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center fade-in">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 gradient-racing rounded-2xl mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-1 17.93c-3.95-.49-7-3.85-7-7.93 0-.62.08-1.21.21-1.79L9 15v1c0 1.1.9 2 2 2v1.93zm6.9-2.54c-.26-.81-1-1.39-1.9-1.39h-1v-3c0-.55-.45-1-1-1H8v-2h2c.55 0 1-.45 1-1V7h2c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2v-.41c2.93 1.19 5 4.06 5 7.41 0 2.08-.8 3.97-2.1 5.39z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Llegamos a todo el país</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Norte, sur, este, oeste. Si está en el mapa, llegamos</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center fade-in">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 gradient-racing rounded-2xl mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M20 2H4c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L2 22l4-4h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V4c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zM6 9h12v2H6V9zm8 5H6v-2h8v2zm4-6H6V6h12v2z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Hablamos tu idioma</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Sin vueltas, sin tecnicismos. Respuestas claras y rápidas</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>